UserPage.Teams: Eamstay inway ichwhay Iway amway away embermay
UserPage.Language: Ethay anguagelay ithway ichwhay Iway antway otay ommunicatecay
UserPage.Instructions.part1: Onway Eflectray, allway orkway isway oneday inway away eamtay. Ifway ouyay antway otay orkway ustjay orfay ourselfyay onway omethingsay, ouyay eednay otay eatecray away ojectpray andway away eamtay inway ichwhay ouyay areway ethay onlyway embermay. Ouyay ancay addway otherway eoplepay atway anyway imetay.
UserPage.Instructions.part2: Inway asecay onay eamtay owsshay upway elowbay, orway ethay "Ogay Erethay" uttonbay ailsfay, easeplay efreshray ouryay owserbray andway ytray againway.
